# Your rule content

- The project uses react-i18next as the i18n solution
- Language configuration files are mainly in @en.json and @zh.json
- Use flat mode for i18n keys e.g., `common.badge.alpha`.
  - _Don't use nested JSON objects._ e.g. `{ common: { badge: { alpha } } }`
